text.__SUMMARY__: Galium proliferum (limestone bedstraw) is a species of plants in the Rubiaceae. It is native to southern California (San Diego + San Bernardino Cos.), southern Nevada (Clark Co.), southern Utah (Kane + Washington Cos.), Arizona, New Mexico, Texas, Coahuila and Nuevo León.
